<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/usc/t7/s8753">Section 8753 of this title</ref>, referred to in par. (3), was repealed by <ref href="/us/pl/113/79/tI/s1101">Pub. L. 113–79, title I, § 1101</ref>, <date date="2014-02-07">Feb. 7, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/658">128 Stat. 658</ref>.</p>
</note>
